            <p class="mb-4 text-xs">A Full-Stack Solution built for Performance and Scale.</p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                <!-- Layer 1 -->
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-24 font-bold text-sky-400 text-sm">FRONTEND</div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-800 p-2 rounded border border-slate-600">
                        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-white">Next.js 16 + React Flow</div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-400">The Visual "Workbench" Interface</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Connector -->
                <div class="pl-32 text-slate-600 text-xs">⬇ HTTPS / JSON</div>
                <!-- Layer 2 -->
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-24 font-bold text-purple-400 text-sm">BACKEND</div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-800 p-2 rounded border border-slate-600">
                        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-white">FastAPI (Python) + Docker</div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-400">Secure Compilation Sandbox & AI Orchestrator</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Connector -->
                <div class="pl-32 text-slate-600 text-xs">⬇ HEX Code</div>
                <!-- Layer 3 -->
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-24 font-bold text-green-400 text-sm">ENGINE</div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-800 p-2 rounded border border-slate-600">
                        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-white">AVR8js (Client-Side)</div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-400">Cycle-Accurate CPU Simulation in Browser</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 07. TECHNICAL HIGHLIGHT: SIMULATION -->
        <div class="board-card">
            <span class="section-number">07</span>
            <h2>Under the Hood: AVR8js</h2>
            <p class="mb-2">We don't just "animate" LEDs. We execute <strong>real Assembly Code</strong>.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                <li><strong class="text-yellow-400">Cycle Accuracy:</strong> The engine simulates the 16MHz clock speed of the Arduino ATmega328P. Delays and timers are precise.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-green-400">Zero Latency:</strong> Once code is compiled, simulation runs locally on the user's machine, requiring no internet bandwidth.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ========================================== -->
    <!-- PAGE 4: THE AI TEACHER (PEDAGOGY) -->
    <!-- ========================================== -->
    <div class="print-page">
        <!-- 08. AI TEACHER MODE -->
        <div class="board-card">
            <span class="section-number">08</span>
            <h2>Generative AI as a "Socratic Tutor"</h2>
            <p>We engineered the AI prompts to avoid "Cheating." The AI is instructed to use the <strong>Socratic Method</strong>—asking questions to guide the student rather than giving answers.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 09. VISUALIZING THE AI LOGIC -->
        <div class="board-card">
            <span class="section-number">09</span>
            <h2>Context-Aware Intelligence</h2>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
                <div class="w-1/3 bg-slate-900 p-2 rounded border border-slate-700">
                    <h3 class="text-xs text-slate-500">INPUT 1: Code</h3>
                    <div class="h-10 bg-slate-800 rounded mt-1"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-1/3 bg-slate-900 p-2 rounded border border-slate-700">
