                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center text-2xl my-1">⬇</div>
            <div class="bg-indigo-900/50 border border-indigo-500 p-3 rounded">
                <h3 class="text-indigo-300">Gemini 2.5 Flash Output</h3>
                <p class="text-xs italic text-indigo-100">"I see your LED is on Pin 9 (Circuit), but your code is toggling Pin 10. Can you match them?"</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 10. PEDAGOGY -->
         <div class="board-card">
            <span class="section-number">10</span>
            <h2>Pedagogical Guardrails</h2>
            <ul class="text-xs space-y-2">
                <li>✅ <strong>Explains Concepts:</strong> "Why do we use a resistor?"</li>
                <li>✅ <strong>Debugs Logic:</strong> "Your loop is blocking because of <code>delay(1000)</code>."</li>
                <li>❌ <strong>Refuses Homework:</strong> "I won't write the code for you, but I will help you start."</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

